  "steps": [
    "Chop spring onion bulbs and greens separately and slice fresh red chilli.",
    "Heat oil in a non-stick wok, add garlic and sauté till light golden brown.",
    "Add spring onion bulbs, fresh red chilli and salt and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken stock and mix well. Once it comes to a boil, add Precia Chicken Momos and cook for 6-8 minutes.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl, sprinkle spring onion greens, drizzle chilli oil and serve hot."
